name: CD34+ CITE-seq dataset (human fetal liver, bone marrow and cord blood) [mRNA]
desc: A CD34+ CITE-seq dataset containing combined single cell RNA and protein data for human fetal BM (n=3, k=8,829, 14-17 PCW), fetal liver (n=4, k=18,904, 9-17 PCW) and cord blood (n=4, k=7,540, 40-42 PCW). This contains 22 discrete progenitor and early-committed cell-states. The protein panel consists of 198 antibodies. *PCW=post-conception weeks
tissue: Fetal Bone Marrow, Fetal Liver, Cord Blood

name: Human fetal BM CITE-seq dataset [PROTEIN]
desc: A CITE-seq dataset containing combined single cell RNA and protein data (k=8,978) for 3 human fetal BM samples at 16-17 post-conception weeks. This contains 32 discrete progenitor, myeloid, lymphoid and stromal cell-states. The protein panel consists of 198 antibodies.
